<div id="txtcont" class="span9" style="position: relative;">
    <p><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='155:181'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '006-1a' );" name="006-1a" class="pb">[006-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='181:189'>欽定四庫全書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='189:210'>　經禮補逸卷六　　　　　元　汪克寛　撰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='210:216'>　　凶禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='216:224'>　　　凶荒禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='224:247'>大司徒以荒政十有二聚萬民一曰散利二曰薄征三</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='247:270'>曰緩刑四曰弛力五曰舎禁六曰去幾七曰眚禮八曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='270:293'>殺哀九曰蕃樂十曰多昬十有一曰索鬼神十有二曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='293:316'>除盜賊士師若邦凶荒則以荒辨之法治之令移民通</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='316:342'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '006-1b' );" name="006-1b" class="pb">[006-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='342:365'>財糾守緩刑朝士若邦凶荒則令邦國都家縣鄙慮刑</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='365:388'>貶遺人掌縣都之委積以待凶荒小宰以法掌朝覲㑹</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='388:411'>同賔客之戒具喪荒亦如之令百官府共其財用喪荒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='411:434'>受其含襚幣玉之事膳夫大荒則不舉司服大荒素服</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='434:457'>大司樂大荒令弛縣典瑞珍圭以恤凶荒小行人若國</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='457:480'>凶荒則令賙委之廩人掌九穀之數若食不能人二鬴</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='480:503'>則令邦移民就穀詔王殺邦用掌客凡禮賔客凶荒殺</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='503:526'>禮司市國凶荒則市無征凡以神仕者以禬國之凶荒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='526:552'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '006-2a' );" name="006-2a" class="pb">[006-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='552:575'>曲禮嵗凶年穀不登君膳不祭肺馬不食穀馳道不除</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='575:598'>祭事不縣大夫不食粱士飲酒不樂玉藻年不順成君</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='598:621'>衣布搢本闗梁不租山澤列而不賦土工不興大夫不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='621:644'>得造車馬春秋傳襄公二十四年大祲之禮君食不兼</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='644:667'>味臺榭不塗弛候廷道不除百官布而不制鬼神禱而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='667:684'>不祀此大祲之禮也王制祭凶年不儉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='684:707'>　愚案祭禮豐年不奢凶年不儉此記禮者之言也孔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='707:730'>　子又曰凶年祀以下牲不同何哉蓋先王之祀制用</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='730:756'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '006-2b' );" name="006-2b" class="pb">[006-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='756:779'>　有常不以嵗之豐凶而易其禮此禮之循乎經也祀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='779:802'>　以下牲如凶年君膳則不舉服則布素樂則弛縣賔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='802:825'>　客則殺禮而以常祭之牲遞降而用者此又禮之通</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='825:848'>　乎變也然嵗有豐凶而禮無奢儉牲有降用而禮無</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='848:860'>　貶損是則未嘗不同也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='860:868'>　　　大札禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='868:891'>大司徒大札則令邦國移民通財舍禁弛力薄征緩刑</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='891:914'>朝士若札喪則令邦國都家縣鄙慮刑貶膳夫大札則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='914:940'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '006-3a' );" name="006-3a" class="pb">[006-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='940:963'>不舉司服大札素服大司樂大札令弛縣司市國札喪</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='963:986'>則市無征掌客凡禮賔客札喪殺禮凡以神仕者以禬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='986:1009'>民之札喪小行人若國札喪則令賻補之均人凶札則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='1009:1017'>無力政無財賦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='1017:1025'>　　　告饑禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='1025:1040'>春秋左傳隱公六年京師來告饑</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='1040:1048'>　　　請糴禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1048:1071'>春秋左傳隱公六年京師來告饑公為之請糴於宋衛</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='1071:1097'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '006-3b' );" name="006-3b" class="pb">[006-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1097:1120'>齊鄭禮也莊公二十八年臧孫辰告糴于齊僖公十三</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1120:1136'>年晉荐饑使乞糴于秦秦輸粟于晉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1136:1144'>　　　歸粟禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1144:1167'>春秋僖公十三年晉荐饑乞糴于秦秦輸粟于晉十五</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1167:1190'>年晉又饑秦又餼之粟定公五年夏歸粟于蔡以周亟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1190:1195'>矜無資</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1195:1203'>　　　大災禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1203:1226'>膳夫大災則不舉司服大災素服大司樂大災令弛縣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1226:1252'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '006-4a' );" name="006-4a" class="pb">[006-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1252:1275'>掌客凡禮賔客禍災殺禮小宗伯大災及執事禱祠于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1275:1298'>上下神祇司巫國有大災則帥巫而造巫恒女巫凡邦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1298:1321'>之大災歌哭而請春秋左傳襄公九年宋災二師令四</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1321:1344'>鄉正敬饗祝宗用馬于四墉祀盤庚于西門之外昭公</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1344:1367'>十八年五月壬午宋衛陳鄭皆大災作鄭子産辭晉公</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1367:1390'>子公孫于東門使司寇出新客禁舊客勿出於宫使子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1390:1413'>寛子上巡羣屏攝至于大宫使公孫登徙大龜使祝史</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='1413:1436'>徙主祏於周廟告于先君使府人庫人各儆其事商成</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='1436:1462'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '006-4b' );" name="006-4b" class="pb">[006-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='1462:1485'>公儆司宫出舊宫人寘諸火所不及司馬司寇列居火</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='1485:1508'>道行火所焮城下之人伍列登城明日使野司寇各保</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='1508:1532'>其徴郊人助祝史除於國北禳火于𤣥冥回禄祈于四</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='1532:1555'>鄘書焚室而寛其征與之材三日哭國不市使行人告</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='1555:1578'>於諸侯宋衛皆如是哀公三年五月辛卯司鐸火火踰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='1578:1601'>公宫桓僖災救火者皆曰顧府南宫敬叔至命周人出</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='1601:1624'>御書俟於宫曰庀汝而不在死子服景伯至命宰人出</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='1624:1647'>禮書以待命命不共有常刑校人乗馬巾車脂轄百官</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='1647:1673'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '006-5a' );" name="006-5a" class="pb">[006-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='1673:1696'>官備府庫慎守宫人肅給濟濡帷幕鬱攸從之蒙葺公</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='1696:1719'>屋自大廟始外内以悛助所不給有不用命則有常刑</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='1719:1742'>無赦公父文伯至命校人駕乗車季桓子至御公立于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='1742:1765'>象魏之外命救火者傷人則止穀梁傳成公五年梁山</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='1765:1788'>崩壅河三日不流晉召伯尊伯尊曰君親素縞帥羣臣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='1788:1811'>而哭之旣而祠焉斯流矣左傳山崩川竭君為之不舉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='1811:1827'>降服乗縵徹出次祝幣史辭而禮焉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='1827:1835'>　　　弔烖禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='1835:1861'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '006-5b' );" name="006-5b" class="pb">[006-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='1861:1884'>小行人若國有烖則令哀弔之春秋左傳宋大水公使</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='1884:1907'>弔焉曰天作淫雨害於粢盛若之何不弔對曰孤實不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='1907:1930'>敬天降之災又以為君憂拜命之辱莊公十一年宋大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='1930:1953'>災襄公三十年宋災叔孫豹㑹晉趙武齊公孫蠆宋向</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='1953:1976'>戍衛北宫佗鄭罕虎及小邾之大夫㑹于澶淵為宋災</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='1976:1999'>故以謀歸宋昭十八年許不弔災君子知許之先亡也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='1999:2022'>雜記廐焚孔子拜鄉人為火來者拜之士壹大夫再亦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='2022:2029'>相弔之道也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='2029:2055'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '006-6a' );" name="006-6a" class="pb">[006-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='2055:2063'>　　　致禬禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='2063:2086'>大宗伯以禬禮哀圍敗大行人致禬以補諸侯之災小</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='2086:2109'>行人若國師役則令槁禬之春秋左傳昭公六年叔弓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='2109:2132'>如楚聘且弔敗也哀公十五年楚子西子期伐吳陳侯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='2132:2155'>使公孫貞子弔焉吳子使太宰嚭勞哀公二十年越圍</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='2155:2178'>吳趙孟降於喪食使楚隆告于吳王曰寡君之老無恤</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='2178:2201'>使陪臣隆敢展謝其不共黄池之役君之先臣志父得</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='2201:2224'>承齊盟曰好惡同之今君在難無恤不敢憚勞非晉國</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='2224:2250'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '006-6b' );" name="006-6b" class="pb">[006-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='2250:2273'>之所能及也使陪臣敢展布之王拜稽首曰寡人不佞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='2273:2296'>不能事越以為大夫憂拜命之辱與之一簞珠使問趙</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='2296:2319'>孟曰句踐將生憂寡人寡人死之不得矣王曰溺人必</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='2319:2342'>笑吾將有問也史黯何以得為君子對曰黯也進不見</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='2342:2365'>惡退無謗言王曰宜哉僖公三十三年公如齊朝且弔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='2365:2371'>有狄師也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='2371:2378'>　　　恤禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='2378:2401'>大宗伯以恤禮哀寇亂春秋左傳昭公二十一年宋華</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='2401:2427'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '006-7a' );" name="006-7a" class="pb">[006-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='2427:2450'>亥向寧華定自陳入于宋南里以叛二十二年薳越使</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='2450:2473'>告于宋曰寡君聞君有不令之臣為君憂無寧以為宗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='2473:2496'>羞寡君請受而戮之對曰孤不佞不能媚其父兄以為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='2496:2519'>君憂拜命之辱襄公十四年衛獻公使子蟜子伯子皮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='2519:2542'>與孫子盟于丘宫孫子皆殺之公如鄄使子行於孫子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='2542:2565'>孫子又殺之公出奔齊孫氏追之敗公徒於阿澤公使</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='2565:2588'>厚成叔弔于衛曰寡君使瘠聞君不撫社稷而越在他</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='2588:2611'>竟若之何不弔以同盟之故使瘠敢私于執事曰有君</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='2611:2637'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '006-7b' );" name="006-7b" class="pb">[006-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='2637:2660'>不弔有臣不敏君不赦宥臣亦不帥職增淫發洩其若</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='2660:2683'>之何衛人使大叔儀對曰羣臣不佞得罪於寡君寡君</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='2683:2706'>不以即刑而悼弃之以為君憂君不忘先君之好辱弔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='2706:2724'>羣臣又重恤之敢拜君命之辱重拜大貺</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='2724:2731'>　　　唁禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='2731:2756'>詩載馳歸唁衛侯春秋穀梁𫝊弔失國曰唁公羊𫝊弔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='2756:2779'>亡國曰唁弔失國曰弔昭公二十五年公孫于齊次于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='2779:2802'>陽州齊侯唁公于野井二十九年公至自乾侯居于鄆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='2802:2828'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '006-8a' );" name="006-8a" class="pb">[006-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='2828:2851'>齊侯使髙張來唁公三十一年晉侯使荀躒唁公于乾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='2851:2875'>侯公羊𫝊昭公二十五年公孫于齊齊侯唁公于野井</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='2875:2898'>曰奈何君去魯國之社稷昭公曰喪人不佞失守魯國</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='2898:2921'>之社稷執事以羞再拜顙髙子執簞食與四脡脯國子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='2921:2944'>執壺漿曰吾寡君聞君在外餕饔未就敢致糗於從者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='2944:2967'>昭公曰君不忘吾先君延及喪人錫之以大禮載拜稽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='2967:2990'>首以衽受髙子曰有夫不祥君無所辱大禮昭公蓋祭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='2990:3013'>而不嘗景公曰寡人有不腆先君之服未之敢服有不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='3013:3039'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0036', 'WYG', '006-8b' );" name="006-8b" class="pb">[006-8b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l143' data-llen='3039:3062'>腆先君之器未之敢用敢以請昭公曰喪人不佞失守</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l144' data-llen='3062:3085'>魯國之社稷執事以羞敢辱大禮敢辭景公曰寡人有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l145' data-llen='3085:3108'>不腆先君之服未之敢服有不腆先君之器未之敢用</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l146' data-llen='3108:3131'>敢固以請昭公曰以吾宗廟之在魯也有先君之服未</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='3131:3154'>之能以服有先君之器未之能以出敢固辭景公曰寡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l148' data-llen='3154:3177'>人有不腆先君之服未之敢服有不腆先君之器未之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l149' data-llen='3177:3200'>敢用請以饗乎從者昭公曰喪人其何稱景公曰孰君</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l150' data-llen='3200:3223'>而無稱昭公於是噭然而哭諸大夫皆哭既哭以遇禮</span><br/>
